title: Neff North Vs. South:  Premier
description: Not knowing that Premier would ever be known outside of Michigan state lines, the shop is named to emulate Supreme. This fact sheds light on the humble beginnings of the Premier store. When you're affiliated with the likes of Josh Kalis, you can be proud on top of humble. Opening in June of 2001, Premier has supplied the people of Michigan with quality skate goods for over ten years.
